iated with using a single source. Moreover, the results\nof the ongoing mechanical durability tests are shown for the current candidate,\nSenSL B/C-Series 60035 SiPMs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 15 Nov 2015 19:48:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 17 Dec 2015 04:01:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-17"}
