portional to the product L.LAMBDA.S dominates, as no\ndirection dependence of the EFG principal component is seen. The lowest order\nterm is isotropic for a cubic symmetry as one has LAMBDA=lambda.1 for cubic\nsystems with the symbol 1 denoting unit operator and lambda being the coupling\nparameter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Nov 2015 12:37:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Mar 2016 17:03:01 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 4 Mar 2016 16:54:48 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 7 Mar 2016 09:05:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-15"}
