esearchers. The results show\nthat there are still many significant differences among each other. Hence,\nbetter correlation should be proposed in the future. The discussion on the\nbasis of the comparison between the previous correlations with the present\nanalytical data is presented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Nov 2015 15:12:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-17"}
